					<div class="entry">
						<div class="w50 right">
				<a href="//www.nytimes.com/times-insider/2015/09/02/from-gaza-to-east-harlem-reporters-notebook/"><img src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2015/08/31/nyregion/01HARLEM4/01HARLEM4-thumbStandard.jpg" width="50" height="50" /></a>
			</div>
						<h5><a href="//www.nytimes.com/times-insider/2015/09/02/from-gaza-to-east-harlem-reporters-notebook/" title="Read: From Gaza to East Harlem: Reporter&#8217;s Notebook">From Gaza to East Harlem: Reporter&#8217;s Notebook</a>
			<span class="postMetaHeaderCommentCount commentCount hidden">
					<i class="icon"></i>
					<a class="commentCountLink commentCountNumberOnly commentCountNoPrompt" href="//www.nytimes.com/times-insider/2015/09/02/from-gaza-to-east-harlem-reporters-notebook/"></a>
				</span>			</h5>
